  "keyFeatures": [
    "LLM-powered conversation summarization with disk caching",
    "Semantic clustering using embeddings and K-means/HDBSCAN",
    "Hierarchical meta-clustering for pattern organization",
    "Dimensionality reduction and interactive visualization",
    "Checkpoint system for processing large datasets",
    "Support for multiple data sources (HuggingFace, Claude, custom)",
    "Built-in web UI for cluster exploration",
    "Extensible architecture with custom models and extractors"
